<%- include('partials/header') %>

<section class="hero about-hero" style="min-height: 50vh; height: auto; display: flex; align-items: center; background: linear-gradient(rgba(3, 19, 56, 0.85), rgba(3, 19, 56, 0.85)), url('/assets/img/hero-gate.jpg') center/cover; padding: 100px 0; text-align: center; position: relative;">
    <div class="container" style="position: relative; z-index: 5;">
        <span class="section-tag" style="background: rgba(211, 140, 63, 0.2); color: #ffd19a; margin-bottom: 20px; display: inline-block;">Our Legacy</span>
        <h1 style="color: #ffffff !important; font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 8vw, 4rem); margin-bottom: 20px; font-weight: 800; text-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);">About the Institute</h1>
        <p style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.95) !important; font-size: 1.25rem; max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; line-height: 1.6;">Championing the developmental and cultural interests of the Niger Delta region.</p>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="section about-content" style="background: var(--primary-dark); color: white; padding: 80px 0;">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="responsive-grid" style="display: grid; gap: 40px; align-items: start;">
            <div class="history-mission">
                <h2 style="color: white; margin-bottom: 30px; font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3rem); font-weight: 700;">Our History & Mission</h2>
                <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; opacity: 0.95; font-size: 1.1rem; text-align: justify;">The Institute for Niger Delta Studies (INDS) was established to serve as a high-level research and advocacy center within Niger Delta University. Our mission is to promote the sustainable development of the Niger Delta through rigorous academic research, policy documentation, and community engagement.</p>
                <p style="line-height: 1.8; opacity: 0.95; font-size: 1.1rem; text-align: justify;">We believe that the challenges of the region—environment, economic equity, and social justice—require intellectual solutions grounded in the local context and cultural realities of our people.</p>
                
                <h3 style="margin-top: 50px; margin-bottom: 25px; color: var(--accent); font-size: 1.8rem;">Institutional Objectives</h3>
                <ul class="objectives-list" style="list-style: none; padding: 0; line-height: 2;">
                    <li style="margin-bottom: 15px; display: flex; gap: 15px; align-items: flex-start;">
                        <i class="fas fa-check-circle" style="color: var(--accent); font-size: 1.4rem; margin-top: 5px;"></i> 
                        <span>To conduct and coordinate research into the history, culture, and environment of the Niger Delta.</span>
                    </li>
                    <li style="margin-bottom: 15px; display: flex; gap: 15px; align-items: flex-start;">
                        <i class="fas fa-check-circle" style="color: var(--accent); font-size: 1.4rem; margin-top: 5px;"></i> 
                        <span>To provide a platform for documentation and preservation of indigenous knowledge systems.</span>
                    </li>
                    <li style="margin-bottom: 15px; display: flex; gap: 15px; align-items: flex-start;">
                        <i class="fas fa-check-circle" style="color: var(--accent); font-size: 1.4rem; margin-top: 5px;"></i> 
                        <span>To organize conferences, seminars, and memorial lectures (like the Melford Okilo series).</span>
                    </li>
                    <li style="margin-bottom: 15px; display: flex; gap: 15px; align-items: flex-start;">
                        <i class="fas fa-check-circle" style="color: var(--accent); font-size: 1.4rem; margin-top: 5px;"></i> 
                        <span>To publish the Research Digest, a peer-reviewed academic journal of regional importance.</span>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="glass-card sidebar-card" style="padding: 40px; border-radius: 24px; background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05); backdrop-filter: blur(20px); border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);">
                <h3 style="color: white; margin-bottom: 30px; font-size: 1.6rem; font-weight: 700;">Leadership</h3>
                <div class="leadership-profile" style="display: flex; gap: 20px; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 35px;">
                    <img src="/assets/img/prof-sibiri.jpg" alt="Director" style="width: 100px; height: 100px; border-radius: 20px; object-fit: cover; border: 3px solid var(--accent); box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);">
                    <div>
                        <h4 style="margin: 0; color: white; font-size: 1.4rem; font-weight: 700;">Prof. A.E. Sibiri</h4>
                        <p style="font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--accent); font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 1px; text-transform: uppercase;">Director, INDS</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; font-style: italic; opacity: 0.9; line-height: 1.8; border-left: 4px solid var(--accent); padding-left: 25px; color: white;">"The Institute stands as a testament to our commitment to ensuring that the voice of the Niger Delta is heard in the halls of global academia."</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>
